AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> "https://dictionary.apa.org/culture") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/EMRO_0004010> "A characteristic of  population reflecting the attitudes, values, and behaviors shared by a particular group within a society, such as a profession, social class, or age group.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/EMRO_0004010> <https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6906-5548>)
